{
  "stem": "27335.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in 1918, the Karoly declared, Hungary's out of the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it actually was a declaration of independence from Austria.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the soldiers, then, yelled in-- in great joy, and someone started to throw their arms away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Karoly, himself-- as a rich man, a rich aristocrat-- send a message out, keep your arms, keep your arms.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because he knew that an independent Hungary will have to defend itself against the Austrians.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was-- he was so right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was in October, 1918.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the following year, 1919, March 21st, came the socialist revolution.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, they generally call it a communist revolution.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It wasn't [INAUDIBLE], but it was really a socialist revolution, with-- under the leadership of Bela Kun, who was also from Trans-- Transylvania-born.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So a Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "As I mentioned, I think the, uh, the intellectuals, and the intellectual was started from [NON-ENGLISH] from [NON-ENGLISH] and so on-- it was in Hungary at the time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Today, it's Romania.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I went to the-- went to Catholic school, because my father was Catholic.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was Protestant-- Calvinist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, but 1918, uh, it was when I was six years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But being the war, and at a six class, public school was only-- only one single, one single teacher.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you could imagine what you could get-- it was practically nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We just attended a school and learned our ABC, and there what was called read anything, practically.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because of that, in 1919, I had to repeat a year-- the first grade in the public school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But then my father, being coming from a sort of a revolutionary family, from [INAUDIBLE] communion, and so on-- well, he was sort of a rebel, a revolutionary.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
